.checkmark::after {
 content: "";

}

}

tabs.tab_title: Q1 :What types of businesses benefit from your video and digital marketing services?
tabs.tab_content: Our services are perfect for real estate agents, event organizers, travel businesses, restaurants, resorts, product brands, and service providers—any business looking to stand out with eye-catching video ads and targeted marketing campaigns.

tabs.tab_title: Q2:How quickly can I get my video ad and campaign live?
tabs.tab_content: Typically, we deliver your video ad within 5-7 business days after the shoot. Campaign setup takes an additional 2-3 days, so you can start seeing leads in under 10 days.

tabs.tab_title: Q3:Do I need to have any marketing experience to work with you?
tabs.tab_content: No experience needed! We handle everything from video production to campaign management. You just tell us your goal—we do the strategy, creative work, and ad execution for you.

tabs.tab_title: Q4:Can I track the performance of my ad campaigns?
tabs.tab_content: Yes, we provide regular performance reports and insights so you can see how many people viewed your ads, engaged with your content, and how many leads you’ve received.
